    "While the metric 'usability' is used in 34 studies (40.5%), the metric 'acceptance' is used in 18 studies (21.4%).",
    "The other most frequently used metrics are listed as follows: 'ease of use' (7 studies, 8.3%), 'satisfaction' (8 studies, 9.5%), 'adherence' (4 studies, 4.8%), 'attitude' (4 studies, 4.8%) and 'experience' (4 studies4.8%).Morrison et al.",
